    "description": "Discipline: Neigong\nSkill: Talent (Any Stringed Instrument) against Evade\nType: Normal\nQi: 1\n\nYou pluck a stringed instrument such as a Guzheng, and create a potent blast of energy harming your foe’s internal organs. This creates a moon-shaped swath of energy that cuts through the air, 5 feet long per Rank of Qi (affecting 1 target per Rank of Qi). Anyone it hits is drained of 1 point of Hardiness per Rank of Neigong. The lost Hardiness is recovered in a single round. Cathartic: This creates a more lasting effect and lost Hardiness must be recovered at the normal rate.",
